{"tid":1146433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲傭偷新加坡僱主2.8萬被捕　監獄掃描器揭發贓款藏私處","createTime":"2019-05-09T08:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T11:37:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e68c3489b3fca75691adc7d89aa81cbefa1f12f8","tid":1146433,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"工人姐姐偷竊僱主財物的案件不時發生，新加坡一名菲律賓女傭偷竊僱主5,002元新幣（約2.8萬港元），僱主發現失竊後報警，女傭涉案被帶走調查，但不肯承認犯案。直至女傭被暫時收押到監獄，才被監獄掃描儀發現原來她將偷竊的贓款收藏在私處，女傭5月9日被判入獄16周。<br />\n新加坡《聯合晚報》報道，涉案被告是28歲菲律賓女傭，她一年前受僱於69歲的商人，主要替商人夫婦及5歲孫子打掃和煮飯。<br />\n法庭指，女傭先後於今年2月和3月偷取僱主的金錢。今年2月，她第一次偷錢但沒有被人發現；今年3月8日，她因家中缺錢用，趁打掃房屋時再偷取僱主放在家中的現金，她利用早前發現的鑰匙和密碼偷偷打開僱主的保險箱，偷走5,002元新加坡幣，再藏在自己的衛生巾。<br />\n事發當天，僱主發現保險箱中的現金失竊，懷疑是女傭偷取後報警。警方接報到場搜查女傭的房間，但到處都找不到失竊的款項，最後將女傭帶走調查，翌日更將女傭控上法庭，法官下令將被告還押樟宜女子監獄。<br />\n女傭被還押到女子監獄當晚接受身體檢查時，身體掃描儀發現她的私處藏有異物，經檢查發現她竟將偷來的5,002元新幣放進小塑料袋，然後塞進私處，企圖帶進監獄瞞天過海。<br />\n女傭最後被控兩項監守自盜和一項觸犯雜項（公共秩序和滋擾）法令的罪狀，最後被判入獄16個星期。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2345000/2346778/thief_thumb_20190509_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2345000%2F2346778%2Fthief_thumb_20190509_S_1024.jpg&h=51dbc8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2346778/%E8%8F%B2%E5%82%AD%E5%81%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB2.8%E8%90%AC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E3%80%80%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E6%8E%83%E6%8F%8F%E5%99%A8%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E8%B4%93%E6%AC%BE%E8%97%8F%E7%A7%81%E8%99%95?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2346778%2F%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%2582%25AD%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%2583%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB2.8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%258D%2584%25E6%258E%2583%25E6%258F%258F%25E5%2599%25A8%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B4%2593%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%25A7%2581%25E8%2599%2595%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=c5743dc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2346778/%E8%8F%B2%E5%82%AD%E5%81%B7%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB2.8%E8%90%AC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E3%80%80%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E6%8E%83%E6%8F%8F%E5%99%A8%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E8%B4%93%E6%AC%BE%E8%97%8F%E7%A7%81%E8%99%95?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"6a5582014c50033262d623bda37eb8918a15253c","tid":1146433,"uid":181801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"D錢臭晒啦"},{"pid":"d2103f5f455d211c1ed6e44483a0ea64c489a09a","tid":1146433,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a5582014c50033262d623bda37eb8918a15253c","tid":1146433,"uid":181801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"D錢臭晒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a49f59191d362fa2c0e9e386476a511762e474","tid":1146433,"uid":34023,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"陰撕紙"},{"pid":"89f2a9bfe06895c85582da5ba99d3ac7579c836e","tid":1146433,"uid":37069,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"陰質錢"},{"pid":"3a84ebd7d65400c11378337d30c84d83668a8f0f","tid":1146433,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:26:23.000Z","msg":"搜唔到錢+唔認都有得拉<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637a019bcb3dee11e0fd05b31022e7573c375a4f","tid":1146433,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8679a64c4c14a2939c9bdd2a70835c685458dd5d","tid":1146433,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a84ebd7d65400c11378337d30c84d83668a8f0f","tid":1146433,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":1